text: CeCe Peniston (born September 6, 1969, in Dayton, Ohio) is an American R&B; singer and former beauty queen. She was very popular in the early 1990s. Her hit song "Finally" was released in 1991. A lot of other songs followed. Peniston was crowned Miss Black Arizona 1989 and Miss Galaxy 1990. == References == Category:American R&B; singers Category:Singers from Ohio Category:1969 births Category:Living people
